Package com.rhizospherejs.gwt.client.bridge

Defines functionality to map bi-directionally between custom POJOs used as representation of Rhizosphere models and equivalent custom-tailored JavaScriptObjects that the underlying Rhizosphere javascript library can understand.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
ModelExtractor<T> Extracts the Java object that was originally used to represent a Rhizosphere model (via Rhizosphere.addModel(Object)) from the JavaScriptObject (used in the visualization Javascript library code) that wraps it.
 

Class Summary
JavaScriptObjectModelBridge A stock ModelBridge to convert model objects which are already defined as JavaScriptObjects.
JsoBuilder Exposes methods that ModelBridge instances can use to convert a POJOs into JavaScriptObject instances that the Rhizosphere javascript library can use as model representations.
JSONObjectModelBridge A stock ModelBridge to convert model objects which are defined as JSONObjects.
JSONStringModelBridge A stock ModelBridge to convert model objects which are defined as JSON Strings.
ModelBridge<T> A ModelBridge is responsible for converting a Java object representing a Rhizosphere model into a JavaScriptObject that the Rhizosphere javascript library can use.
 

Package com.rhizospherejs.gwt.client.bridge Description

Defines functionality to map bi-directionally between custom POJOs used as representation of Rhizosphere models and equivalent custom-tailored JavaScriptObjects that the underlying Rhizosphere javascript library can understand.
